name: MS Real Lite - Skindentation & Wide Hips LoRA
description:
Do you want to support me? Consider being a patron on Patreon to vote on train polls and access stuff early. ❤️

For personal reasons I decided on creating 2 versions of the models. Lite and Full ones

Lite models are less trained versions of the Full models but yet usable ones. Full models will be on Patreon and after 1-2 week span I'll release Full models on our discord server.

Trained with 100 images and 768x768.

Use 512x and hires fix for better results

Tags you might need are

1girl, solo, skindentation, thighhighs, thighs, panties, ass, standing, wide hips, thick thighs

Use the LoRA weight around 0.8 and 1 for the best results

Discord server feel free to drop and say hi ^^
